node.text:
Happy Friday! We’re open today 12-10p 

Space Cookie Bites
Special Bite-Size Cookie IPA brewed with cookies, milk sugar, vanilla beans, and dry hopped with dank hops. A more crushable cookie!  In sweet collaboration with @omnipollo. 7.4% ABV (Note: Contains Dairy)

Ties
Saison brewed with buckwheat and aged in french oak wine barrels for 9 months. Bottled conditioned in 750ml cork & caged champagne bottles for an additional 16 months. 5.9% ABV. Lively and lovely! 

Food truck: @felicecatering 🍕

Today (Wed) we’re open 12-7p for walkups and curbside with a new addition to the menu:

Even More Hipsterish - DDH IPA
A collaboration with @eviltwinbrewing . A bigger and hoppier version of our previous Hipsterish pale ale collab. Double Dry Hopped (DDH) IPA with Nelson Sauvin, Citra, and Simcoe. 7.0%

And yesterday’s:
Foggy Window - DIPA
Classic Monk Double IPA with Citra, Nelson Sauvin, and Galaxy 8.1%

🚚 Beer Shipping available (CA only).

node.text:
Two new beers today. Open 12-7p for walkups and curbside 

CHECKED-IN LUGGAGE 🧳🧶  A collaboration with @fastfashionbeer // Double Dry Hopped (DDH) Double IPA with PHANTASM and DDH’d with Nelson Sauvin, Citra, and Cascade hops. Phantasm is a new product from New Zealand derived from Malborough Sauvignon grape skins that are rich in tropical fruity “thiols”  (aromatic compounds). Thanks to @phantasm.nz for thinking of us to explore this tropical-boosting Phantasm!  8.2% ABV 

BABBLESHIP 👅🛳  Double Dry Hopped (DDH) Double IPA with Galaxy and Mosaic hops 8.2% ABV

🚚 Beer Shipping (CA only) available.
